An extension over Jeff Winkler's original ([1]) nosy to do personnal CI.

Features:
* automatically run nosetest whenever one of the monitored files has changed
* notify using Gnome's notification library
* per project configuration to override defaults

Usage:
* install in path and run nosy.py
* optionaly create a .nosy file in your local directory

Alternatives:
* another improved version of nosy [2]

Links
[1] http://jeffwinkler.net/2006/04/27/keeping-your-nose-green/
[2] http://douglatornell.ca/software/python/Nosy-1.0.tar.gz
